---
title: Roasted Pumpkin Soup with Pecan & Ciabatta Croutons
description: Are you the kind of person that wishes they could have dessert for dinner? Lucky for you, we’ve concocted this savoury soup with all the highlights of pumpkin and pecan pies. It’s rich and nutty (pssst… our secret is roasting the pumpkin to bring out its amazing natural sweetness!).
